data.description: Welcome home!  This open and spacious home is perfect for you.  The interior features many upgrades, including beautiful shiplap walls in the living and dining rooms, kitchen island, primary bathroom and also in the laundry room.  Other charming features include archways throughout, easy to maintain tile floors, warm wood toned floors in the bedrooms, updated hardware in the kitchen, a custom pantry and a walk-in Laundry Room.  There's views of the back yard from the kitchen, dining room, living room, and master bedroom.  The master bedroom is spacious, elegant, and it has a spacious walk in closet.  The master bathroom features a step-in shower, modern mirrors, and custom shiplap.  Off-street parking is available in the two car garage, which has epoxy floor. Enjoy the outdoors on the screened lanai, underneath your pergola, and beautifully maintained, fully fenced yard!  The awesome community features a zero entry pool, community center, several ponds, fountains and plenty of green areas.  Sellers are willing to assist with Buyer's closing costs.
